<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 14 May 2026 02:01:16 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>重新连接特定电路的工程大脑“旁路”可以增强抗压能力</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/engineered-brain-bypass-that-rewires-specific-circuits-could-boost-resilience-to-stress</link><description>大脑回路的损坏或破坏会导致许多神经系统疾病。杜克大学医学院开发的一种新的定制生物“线路”为新的治疗方法指明了道路——绕过损坏的大脑连接，而不是依赖长期药物或外部刺激。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/engineered-brain-bypass-that-rewires-specific-circuits-could-boost-resilience-to-stress.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 May 2026 02:01:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/engineered-brain-bypass-that-rewires-specific-circuits-could-boost-resilience-to-stress</guid></item><item><title>通过生酮饮食瞄准全身和肿瘤代谢平衡可增强 FLT3-ITD 急性髓系白血病的治疗效果</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/targeting-systemic-and-tumor-metabolic-balances-with-ketogenic-diets-enhance-efficacy-of-therapy-in-flt3-itd-acute-myeloid-leukemia</link><description>古皮耶等人。描述了一种针对 FLT3 突变白血病宿主和肿瘤初级代谢的替代方法。生酮饮食策略旨在平衡脂质稳态，增强脂肪酸和氨基酸降解活性，减弱靶向治疗后的FLT3信号激活、细胞增殖和白血病进展。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/targeting-systemic-and-tumor-metabolic-balances-with-ketogenic-diets-enhance-efficacy-of-therapy-in-flt3-itd-acute-myeloid-leukemia2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 May 2026 01:46:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/targeting-systemic-and-tumor-metabolic-balances-with-ketogenic-diets-enhance-efficacy-of-therapy-in-flt3-itd-acute-myeloid-leukemia</guid></item><item><title>未来：顶尖大学的研究新闻</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/futurity-research-news-from-top-universities</link><description>基于大脑功能的未来计算机。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/futurity-research-news-from-top-universities.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 May 2026 01:31:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/futurity-research-news-from-top-universities</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯正在建造星际旅行的引擎，而近三分之二的农村家庭仍然没有室内管道——这一差距说明了太空项目如何实际获得资金的重要问题</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/russia-is-building-engines-for-interstellar-travel-while-nearly-two-thirds-of-rural-households-still-have-no-indoor-plumbing-and-that-gap-says-something-important-about-how-space-programs-ac</link><description>2026 年 2 月，Rosatom 宣布推出一款等离子火箭发动机原型，科学家声称该发动机可以将前往火星的旅行时间从八个月缩短到三十天。该发动机在特罗伊茨克的专用设施中制造，并在旨在模拟深空的 14 米真空室中进行了测试，使用电磁场将氢电离成[...]。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/russia-is-building-engines-for-interstellar-travel-while-nearly-two-thirds-of-rural-households-still-have-no-indoor-plumbing-and-that-gap-says-something-important-about-how-space-programs-ac.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 May 2026 01:16:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/russia-is-building-engines-for-interstellar-travel-while-nearly-two-thirds-of-rural-households-still-have-no-indoor-plumbing-and-that-gap-says-something-important-about-how-space-programs-ac</guid></item><item><title>构建移动中跟踪质子的超导量子电路</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/building-a-superconducting-quantum-circuit-that-follows-protons-on-the-go</link><description>耶鲁大学两个实验室发明的一种新设备可以模拟量子质子“隧道效应”，这是化学和生物学中常见的一种普遍现象。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/building-a-superconducting-quantum-circuit-that-follows-protons-on-the-go3.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 May 2026 01:01:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/building-a-superconducting-quantum-circuit-that-follows-protons-on-the-go</guid></item><item><title>人工智能是伟大的过滤器</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/ai-is-the-great-filter</link><description>&l